      "title": "The President informs the Prime Minister that he agrees with the decisions taken at the party leaders' meeting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has informed Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe that he will agree to any decision taken at the party leaders' meeting to be held this afternoon.",
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena has called a special party leaders meeting today at 4:00 pm to resolve the ongoing crisis."
      ],
